---
---
<section class="hero-wrap">
  <div class="page">
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">
        <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
        <span class="eyebrow-text">Cyber Intelligence for Financial Leaders</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Strategic risk<br>intelligence for <em>decision-makers.</em></h1>
      <p>High-signal cybersecurity briefings written for CISOs, executives, and board members navigating governance, compliance, and emerging threats in financial services.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-wrap {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .hero {
    padding: 80px 0;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .eyebrow-line {
    width: 28px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--coral);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .eyebrow-text {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--coral);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 52px;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--heading);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--coral);
  }

  .hero p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--body-text);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 600px;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }
</style>
